\"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Lincoln\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Lincoln\"}, {\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.8160344807485264, \"rank\": 0.22543757384533336, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hachette_Book_Group\", \"score\": 0.825534069808973, \"rank\": 0.1990384480819631, \"text\": \"Poppy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hachette_Book_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hachette_Book_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Come late June at the Jamaica Athletics Administrative Association (JAAA) National Championships, she could be facing many-time national champion and national record holder Natoya Goule; 1,500m record holder Adelle Tracey; and former quarter-miler Chrisann Gordon-Powell for a spot on the team to the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 956, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamaica Athletics Administrative Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica_Athletics_Administrative_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natoya_Goule\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Natoya Goule\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natoya_Goule\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natoya_Goule\"}, {\"begin\": 1142, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelle_Tracey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adelle Tracey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelle_Tracey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelle_Tracey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, by then Beckford would have run the qualifying time of 1:59.30.\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1267, \"end\": 1275, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"score\": 0.6738800821846135, \"rank\": 0.4839435478760923, \"text\": \"Beckford\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A week after she ran a personal best 52.79 seconds to win the 400m at the 41st Victor Lopez Classic, Beckford lowered her 800m outdoors personal best from 2:05.88.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1410, \"end\": 1415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brook_Lopez\", \"score\": 0.9727986263914615, \"rank\": 0.02793125268962759, \"text\": \"Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brook_Lopez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brook_Lopez\"}, {\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"score\": 0.6738800821846135, \"rank\": 0.4839435478760923, \"text\": \"Beckford\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also went under the previous school record 2:03.80 set 32 years ago by Theresa Dunn-Fuqua.\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1562, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theresa_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"score\": 0.999997641000445, \"rank\": 2.3590013973794306e-06, \"text\": \"Theresa\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theresa_Lopez-Fitzgerald\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Theresa_Lopez-Fitzgerald\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this month, after failing to get past the first round at the NCAA Indoor National Championships, Beckford, who was named Big12 Indoor track and field performer of the year, told theJamaica Observershe was focused on qualifying for the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999839583490235, \"rank\": 1.6041406457393267e-05, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999980834673, \"rank\": 1.9165136055235378e-09, \"text\": \"National Championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_National_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1696, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"score\": 0.6738800821846135, \"rank\": 0.4839435478760923, \"text\": \"Beckford\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything is going pretty good.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have just been training hard\\u2026and I am just going to go back to training, train hard to stay focused.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am hoping to make the Olympic team this year, this is my main goal,\\\" Beckford said, looking ahead to what is expected to be a gruelling outdoor season.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"score\": 0.6738800821846135, \"rank\": 0.4839435478760923, \"text\": \"Beckford\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was brutally frank about her performance at the NCAA Indoor National where she finished 14th overall with 2:06.55.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2186, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999839583490235, \"rank\": 1.6041406457393267e-05, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have no idea what happened, my head was just not in it today,\\\" she said before adding she was ready to make amends in the outdoor season.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": []}]}"